      "title": "Future Tense Basics",
      "titleLT": "Būsimasis laikas",
      "explanation": "To express future, add the prefix 'be-' or use future endings -siu, -si, -s. For example: 'skaityti' → 'skaitysiu' (I will read).",
      "examples": [
        {
          "lithuanian": "Aš skaitysiu knygą.",
